g src=http://www.boomspeed.com/shiken/shinsai1_th.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 51 Paladin Upgrade Questions</span><hr size=1> Head: Deepwater<br>Rings: Velium Fire Wedding Rings (6ac 65hp each)<br>Face: Crystal Spider Eyes<br>Wrists: Ice Forged Shackle, Deepwater<br>Chest: Enamelled Black Chestplate <br>Shoulders: Tattered Mantle, Adamantite Epolets<br>Hands: Gauntlets of the Black <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/unorpin.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Norpin</A> at: 4/14/02 7:48:50 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uangelsyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Angelsyn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Blessed Protector</span><br>  Posts: 316<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/14/02 2:36:00 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=494.topic&index=2>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: 51 Paladin Upgrade Questions</span><hr size=1> Here it comes again... <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START ;) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/wink.gif ALT=";)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <br><br>Enchanted/Imbued Brellium Plate.... find Stats here: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://www.eqtraders.com/secrets/recipes_smithing_armor_stats.htm#dwarven">www.eqtraders.com/secrets...tm#dwarven</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>Find place to look for a Smith, here: <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub13.ezboard.com/feqtraderscornerfrm21">pub13.ezboard.com/feqtraderscornerfrm21</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br><br>Other than that...<br><br>1) Mask with AC.  Cougarskin Mask is free and easy.<br>2) Symbol of Marr for the Neck, if you go on a PoA raid.<br>3) Gauntlets of the Black are better than DW, 9 times out of 10.  Thunder-etched Gauntlets from Kael if you can get them.<br>4) Ro Boots are better than DWBs.<br>5) Sell the RMB to a Druid/Shaman and get something with AC.  Bracer of Scavenging, Ice Forged Shackles, Ry'Gorr Bracer, DW Bracer... sell the other bracer too.<br>6) Tattered Mantle or Crested Spaulders for the Shoulders.<br>7) 6/65 rings, possibly get a Shadel Bandit Ring.<br><!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Deepwater Helm<br>9) Enamelled Black Chestplate or Barbed Ringmail BP.<br>10) Spider Fur Cloak or the White Bear Pelt cloak from Kael.<br><br>Overall, I think you're going to be better off with the Enchanted/Imbued Brellium Plate, but you're looking at paying 2-8kpp per piece due to the rarity of Temper drops, the cost of Imbued Rubies, the cost of Enchanter time to enchant the Brellium &amp; the high level of skill required.<br><br>However, just look at that stuff!  It's worth the price for most pieces.<br><br>Edit: Most helpful pieces for you...  Bracers, Boots, Pauldrons, Greaves, Cloak &amp; Breastplate. <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uangelsyn.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Angelsyn</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.aol.com/tdlutenatenjou/icon_keyne.jpg" BORDER=0> at: 4/14/02 2:38:27 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/uflintrok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Flintrok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Noble Squire</span><br>  Posts: 12<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(4/15/02 6:22:21 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub13.ezboard.com/fpaladinsofnorrathfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=494.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valig